<link rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' href='blog.css'><script language='javascript' src='javascript/include.js'></script><h3>The dawn of time</h3>
<div class='postDate'>Thursday, 27 April 2006</div>



<p class='postBody'>
 Well, not quite, but the dawn of the <i>Prism</i> blog, "In between issues". Here we'll try to keep you up to date with happenings, as well as muse on various things, including life outside <i>Prism</i>.<br />
<br />
I aim to have a post a day for this first week, and at least one or two posts a week after that.<br />
<br />
Anyone at all can comment on these posts, so please do so. And when there's interesting stuff here, email the link to your friends so they can comment too!
</p>

